paint.shared.objects

Class ExperimentInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • paint.shared.objects.ExperimentInfo

  • public class ExperimentInfo
extends Object
    Represents metadata and associated data objects for a single experiment.

    This class encapsulates both the descriptive metadata and the related data structures (squares, tracks, and tables) that define one recording in the PAINT workflow.
